 in reshumot the official gazette other the holder of a petroleum right is entitled to import into israel free of customs duties and other import levies the goods required by him for petroleum exploration purposes leasee is liable for a royalty of oneeighth   of the quantity of petroleum produced and saved from the lease area ministry of national infrastructures home company projects news investor info contact us disclaimer copyright adira energy     designed and powered by blender media financial statements  adira energy tsxv adl otcbb adenf frankfurt aorlb home company about us board of directors management team corporate directory code of conduct careers projects israel oil  gas offshore yitzhak license technical reports news       investors stock information financial statements share structure media presentation fact sheet upcoming events agm materials contact   view our presentation investor info stock information financial statements share structure media presentation fact sheet upcoming events agm materials financial statements international financial reporting standards ifrs  june   interim financial statements mda   march   interim financial statements mda      december   audited consolidated financial statements mda aif september   interim consolidated financial statements mda   june   interim financial statements mda   march   interim financial statements mda      december   audited consolidated financial statements mda aif september   interim consolidated financial statements mda   june   interim consolidated financial statements mda   march   interim financial statements mda      december   audited consolidated financial statements mda aif september   interim consolidated financial statements mda   june   interim consolidated financial statements mda   march   interim financial statements mda      december   audited consolidated financial statements mda     canadian generally accepted accounting principles gaap  december   interim consolidated financia